name: Arcade Bonanza
overview: Compilation of three games, Ribbit! (which is a re-labeled Froggie from Ed Fries, used without his permission), Rescue Sub, and Bug Out. Keypunch as a publisher used repackaged or relabeled software on many disks, as was done here. This release is not the same contents as the MS-DOS release of the same name by Keypunch, although both feature Frogger clones.
